---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageTitle: Clash Verge 使用文章与配置指南
description: 汇总 Clash Verge 安装、下载、配置、设备连接与日常使用文章。
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 12
  alias: posts
permalink: "/blog/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
---
<main class="light-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow" style="color:#0f5db8;">Clash Verge Blog</p>
        <h1 class="page-title-white">Clash Verge 使用文章与配置指南</h1>
        <p>围绕桌面端、移动端、订阅管理和日常连接整理可阅读的内容。</p>
      </div>
      <a class="soft-button" style="color:#152033;" href="/download.html">下载中心</a>
    </div>
    <div class="post-list">
      {% for post in posts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <a class="post-image-link" href="{{ post.url }}" aria-label="打开 {{ post.data.title }}">
          <img src="https://tse-mm.bing.com/th?q={{ post.data.imageKeyword or post.data.title | urlencode }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }} 配图" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | dateText }}</time>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <div class="tags">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
            {% if tag != "posts" %}<span>{{ tag }}</span>{% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
